---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Merry Christmas everyone!! Ever since I have watched Violet Evergarden Episode 7, I knew I have to transcribed that emotional soundtrack. I'm pretty satisfied with the end result, although there is definitely room for improvement. 

Hope y'all enjoy it and have a great holiday :)

If you like this video, please tell your friend, family or anyone to listen to this song. I will appreciate a lot if you do so! Hope you enjoy the sheet and stay tune for the next video.
